service.arf.reasoner
Interface Reasoner

All Superinterfaces:
Optimiser, Solver, Validator
All Known Implementing Classes:
AlloySATReasoner, DesigntimeReasoner, FaMaReasonerActivator, PartitioningReasoner, RandomConfigurationReasoner, RandomPathReasoner, RandomReasoner, ReasonerBundleActivator, ReasonerService, RuntimeReasoner
public interface Reasoner
extends Optimiser, Solver, Validator

The reasoner interface provides all three tasks of a reasoner. Therefore it extends the interfaces Optimiser, Solver and Validator.
